{"tid":1780482,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[半考古] 有冇手足有玩 L A Noire?","createTime":"2019-12-12T11:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T14:07:11.000Z","uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8291779e8adaa092dce2de9a73a4903f37fe85d","tid":1780482,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da69df93426720b72e058667f122d71128c64832","tid":1780482,"uid":323588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"想玩好耐但係永遠miss曬啲特價，又唔記得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475d61bdc696cf294a2ad74adef5d29ee268a9f4","tid":1780482,"uid":115084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:23:15.000Z","msg":"上年steam特價幾十蚊買左黎玩<br />\n因為查案game啲英文都唔係常見字，費事玩得咁辛苦所以down左漢化patch黎玩<br />\n一路玩覺得主角同佢個班退役軍人好慘，為國出力但係返到黎唔係有心理創傷就係待遇好差，差唔多個個都無咩好下場<br />\n隻game都將左LA當年治安差同官商勾結既景像描繪得幾好<br />\n結局查黑色大理花單案幾緊張幾正，特別最後要落地牢追個犯自己一個玩幾驚下(我好細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最後主角結局都好唏噓<br />\n但講返審犯個度我覺得d表情勁難睇囉，好似佢話係咁就係咁，呢方面我覺得detroit become human做得比較好，當然咁比係唔多公平既(講返追犯同打鬥我返而覺得L.A.Noir做得好玩啲)<br />\n最後我覺得如果鍾意睇劇情同rpg game呢隻值得玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef63bbc57aeb0cc763348d3e0fb88e5e6d25eb5","tid":1780482,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da69df93426720b72e058667f122d71128c64832","tid":1780482,"uid":323588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"想玩好耐但係永遠miss曬啲特價，又唔記得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:03:25.000Z","msg":"放入wishlist等特價啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n唔想洗太多錢買,等下囉惟有...<br />\n好似RDR2我恨左好耐,但連DLC要6百真係唔捨得...<br />\n但我真係好想玩呀屌 (雖然已經唔HIT)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3080ca7e8dd896179704c87bc6bea7a00620d2c","tid":1780482,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"玩過<br />\n個地圖好大<br />\n但好似度度一樣咁"},{"pid":"6def36b29c7b70464a4af22dca96dc79d00f1af8","tid":1780482,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"475d61bdc696cf294a2ad74adef5d29ee268a9f4","tid":1780482,"uid":115084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T14:23:15.000Z","msg":"上年steam特價幾十蚊買左黎玩<br />\n因為查案game啲英文都唔係常見字，費事玩得咁辛苦所以down左漢化patch黎玩<br />\n一路玩覺得主角同佢個班退役軍人好慘，為國出力但係返到黎唔係有心理創傷就係待遇好差，差唔多個個都無咩好下場<br />\n隻game都將左LA當年治安差同官商勾結既景像描繪得幾好<br />\n結局查黑色大理花單案幾緊張幾正，特別最後要落地牢追個犯自己一個玩幾驚下(我好細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最後主角結局都好唏噓<br />\n但講返審犯個度我覺得d表情勁難睇囉，好似佢話係咁就係咁，呢方面我覺得detroit become human做得比較好，當然咁比係唔多公平既(講返追犯同打鬥我返而覺得L.A.Noir做得好玩啲)<br />\n最後我覺得如果鍾意睇劇情同rpg game呢隻值得玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"真心正GAME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得審犯唔係難睇咁簡單,而係唔合理、好唔consistent。<br />\n個犯D表情閃縮,點睇都係身有屎,點知又話佢講真話;另一個犯差唔多表情又話佢講大話。好似有個毒品拆家分明講大話,evidence應該就係之前有個賣加料爆谷巴人既供詞,但佢都係話答錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔計呢點,真心好鍾意佢營造二戰後既感覺。人性黑暗面、官商黑勾結、辦公室政治(明明告兩個都可能,但唔告個共產主義作家就會勁低分)、冷戰,呢D野佢唔會避。<br />\n<br />\n最最欣賞係隻GAME唔會搞埋D主角光環。主角唔會無敵、唔會啱晒,佢都會錯、會許志安、會林奠(剛愎自用),呢樣日本game真係要改善下...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 入地牢追個serial killer個mission我都有少少驚(笑),不過我好鍾意呢個CASE(除左估地標之外...)同d partners (除左Roy)。"},{"pid":"267a6160b89d34061922e305b8b6f95fbe3d68cd","tid":1780482,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3080ca7e8dd896179704c87bc6bea7a00620d2c","tid":1780482,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"玩過<br />\n個地圖好大<br />\n但好似度度一樣咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"確實度度一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘除周圍捉賊(細CASE)之外,冇咩其他特別野可以做...<br />\n覺得少少晒左個地圖。"},{"pid":"c3c99cb2fd4f197aa68755388bf19362ce590342","tid":1780482,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da69df93426720b72e058667f122d71128c64832","tid":1780482,"uid":323588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"想玩好耐但係永遠miss曬啲特價，又唔記得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"下星期sales應該會減"},{"pid":"9424c57f8f3c58caf83a536bc87ee11fea273a7d","tid":1780482,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"最近玩左Sherlock Holmes系列，等有減買呢隻玩"},{"pid":"665ccd0dcefc5dd2399fde2d3c7b68c216e1e34b","tid":1780482,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9424c57f8f3c58caf83a536bc87ee11fea273a7d","tid":1780482,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"最近玩左Sherlock Holmes系列，等有減買呢隻玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"正嘛ching? 好似幾吸引咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1053e78e117f13d5fbede8ed9ef776933f649d2b","tid":1780482,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"665ccd0dcefc5dd2399fde2d3c7b68c216e1e34b","tid":1780482,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9424c57f8f3c58caf83a536bc87ee11fea273a7d","tid":1780482,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"最近玩左Sherlock Holmes系列，等有減買呢隻玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"正嘛ching? 好似幾吸引咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:07:11.000Z","msg":"我暫時淨係玩左testament同crimes and punishments,因為呢兩隻評價最高。<br />\ntestament同前作玩法主要係執道具，合道具同諗下道具點用。仲有解謎題同deduction board 組織案情。謎題難度適中而且有得skip(不過冇成就)。故事一般，唔係特別精彩，不過都算合理既。c&amp;p打後都大改玩法。c&amp;p變左6單獨立案件。d謎題少左同易玩左好多，但重點變左去deduction board度，得出唔同結論可以觸發唔同結局(當然正確答案得一個)，又有得道德抉擇揀放唔放過兇手。真係有得畀你推理真相本身係幾有趣，但問題有d case根本唔多合理，而且好多時都唔係證據確鑿，你只係估邊個係大d機會係兇手。加上冇主線故事得獨立案件。"}]}